OL,3,CArtist's final work gifted to eye
OL,4,Csurgeon who saved his sight
OL,6,FJulie Harrison went to view Tom Hume's
OL,7,Fpainting as it was gifted to Maged
OL,8,FHabib by his wife Barbara
OL,10,FAn artist's final work has been gifted
OL,11,Fto the eye surgeon who saved his sight.
OL,13,FTom Hume completed the painting in
OL,14,FAugust last year and planned to
OL,15,Fpresent it to his doctor.
