OL,3,CArtist's final work gifted to eye
OL,4,Csurgeon who saved his sight
OL,6,FBut he died suddenly before he could
OL,7,Fgive the piece to consultant
OL,8,Fophthalmologist and retinal surgeon,
OL,9,FMaged Habib, suffering a cardiac
OL,10,Farrest while swimming in Seaham
OL,11,FHarbour in October.
OL,13,FHis wife, Barbara, has now gifted the
OL,14,Fartwork herself to the Sunderland Eye
OL,15,FInfirmary specialist, to ensure her
OL,16,Fhusband's wishes were followed.
OL,18,FPictures taken by artist Tom Hume
OL,19,Fbefore his death show the progress of
OL,20,Fhis painting taking shape
