OL,3,CArtist's final work gifted to eye
OL,4,Csurgeon who saved his sight
OL,6,FShe told ITV Tyne Tees: "When I
OL,7,Frealised that was Tom's last finished
OL,8,Fpainting, my temptation was to just
OL,9,Fnot tell anybody and for me to keep it.
OL,11,F"But I knew he had done it for a very
OL,12,Fimportant reason and he did want to
OL,13,Fshow the skill and the bravery of the
OL,14,Fpeople who worked at the (Sunderland)
OL,15,FRoyal Infirmary.
OL,17,F"It was the best way Tom knew how to
OL,18,Fshow his appreciation, by offering his
OL,19,Fskill back in return for a skill
OL,20,Foffered to him and it was a pleasure
OL,21,Fto do it."
