OL,3,CArtist's final work gifted to eye
OL,4,Csurgeon who saved his sight
OL,6,FThe artwork had been named Kosthalmic,
OL,7,Fa blend of cosmic and ophthalmic.
OL,8,FNotes in Mr Hume's sketchbook referred
OL,9,Fto the image as an eye and the design
OL,10,Falso drew on the structure of outer
OL,11,Fspace.
OL,13,F"It is really very moving and very
OL,14,Fhumbling to see a patient who is very
OL,15,Fhappy and grateful and pleased to show
OL,16,Fhis appreciation with such a beautiful
OL,17,Fpainting," Dr Habib said.
OL,19,F"It takes a long time to develop. It
OL,20,Fis what we feel all about our
OL,21,Frelationship with our patients.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
