OL,3,CArtist's final work gifted to eye
OL,4,Csurgeon who saved his sight
OL,6,F"It is not only about treating them it
OL,7,Fis about becoming friends and this is
OL,8,Fsuch a humbling experience for me."
OL,9,FThe painting will be kept at Dr
OL,10,FHabib's home in the short term but
OL,11,Fthere are plans to make it the pride
OL,12,Fof place of the new eye infirmary when
OL,13,Fit opens in two years.
